V0501_01_00_00_0.text: A Dueltainer's job is to put on a show you'll never forget!

V0501_01_00_01_0.text: No matter who I face, I'll keep Dueling my Duel!

V0501_01_00_02_0.text: This Duel deserves nothing less than my 100%!

V0501_01_00_03_0.text: Dueling is the best way to spread joy throughout the world!

V0501_01_00_03_1.text: And that's what I'll do when I swing into action!

V0501_01_00_04_0.text: I'll Dueltain like my Dad to flip your frown upside down!

V0501_03_00_00_0.text: We're getting to the best part of the Duel!

V0501_03_00_01_0.text: Time for the climax of this extravaganza!

V0501_03_00_04_0.text: I gotta have heart if I want to win!

V0501_03_00_05_0.text:
I'm taking control of this Duel!
Starting now!

V0501_05_00_00_0.text:
It all comes down to this!
One final card for everything!

V0501_06_01_03_0.text: Sure you want to do that?

V0501_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0501_07_09_01_0.text: Check out the card I set!

V0501_11_01_00_0.text: I summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0501_11_08_01_0.text:
I build the Overlay Network!
Xyz Summon!

V0501_11_09_01_0.text:
Swing far, Pendulum!
Carve the arc of victory!

V0501_11_09_01_1.text:
My monsters are ready to swing into action!
Pendulum Summon!

V0501_16_00_00_0.text:
It's time for the big finale!
So let's end it with a bang!

V0501_21_00_00_0.text: That brings my turn to an end.

V0501_21_00_03_0.text: Can't wait to see what you do!

V0501_21_00_04_0.text:
Can't let this show end yet!
I have more surprises in store!

V0501_21_00_05_0.text: I'm only fine with losing if I know I gave it my all.

V0501_28_00_00_0.text: That's what Dueltaining is all about!

V0501_28_00_01_0.text: This is the kind of Dueling that I always wanted to do.

V0501_28_00_02_0.text:
Dad...
Do you think I'm getting as good as you?

V0501_28_00_03_0.text: I want everyone to enjoy the Duel - especially my opponent!

V0501_28_00_04_0.text: By Dueltaining like my Dad, I hope I made you smile!

V0501_28_00_05_0.text: Zuzu's training hard to improve her game, so I have to too!

V0501_29_00_00_0.text: I can't be sad when a Duel was this awesome!

V0501_29_00_01_0.text:
Always have fun - whether you win or lose.
That's my motto!

V0501_29_00_02_0.text:
Wow!
Every move you made was one step ahead of mine!

V0501_29_00_03_0.text:
My game isn't cutting it.
I gotta get a lot stronger.

V0501_29_00_04_0.text: If I Dueltain like this, I can't even make a hyena laugh.

V0501_29_00_05_0.text: You've shown me how I can take Pendulum to the next level!

V0501_33_00_00_0.text: This is me at the top of my game!

V0501_33_00_02_0.text: We all can Dueltain, but only I can Dueltain like this!

V0501_30_00_01_0.text: I'm ready to swing into action!

V0501_30_00_02_0.text: The spectacular Pendulum Show is about to begin!

V0501_34_00_00_0.text: Instead of shrinking in fear, put yourself out there!

V0501_34_00_01_0.text: Don't let your heart be in Defense Position!

V0501_34_00_02_0.text: Stop! This isn't what Dueling should be!

V0501_34_00_03_0.text: How can I entertain anyone if I don't like how I Duel?

V0501_34_00_04_0.text: Don't use Dueling as a weapon!

V0501_34_00_05_0.text: Basic boring strategies won't fire up the crowd!

V0501_34_00_06_0.text: I Duel to make everyone happy.

V0501_34_00_09_0.text:
Don't Duel for revenge!
Or you'll be fighting forever!

V0501_34_00_10_0.text: I'm here to make everyone smile - starting with you!
